        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1865874319" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16166972719173357966">I finally finished this one! Thanks to retail (ironically in a bookstore) holding me back from getting this completed faster.<br/><br/>I didn&apos;t enjoy this as much as Lost Gods but it was still a great journey with wonderful mythology.<br/><br/><img alt='Image result for peter pan fan art dark' src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1577285960i/28667363.jpg' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/></span>
  <span id="freeText16166972719173357966" style="display:none">I finally finished this one! Thanks to retail (ironically in a bookstore) holding me back from getting this completed faster.<br><br>I didn't enjoy this as much as Lost Gods but it was still a great journey with wonderful mythology.<br><br><img alt="Image result for peter pan fan art dark" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1577285960i/28667363.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br></span>
